{"type": "article", "id": 11210, "title": "The WABI-SABI Mirror &Table 镜子和桌子", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-25T07:27:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135752gx9kBnoXdESuJ4Zl.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<span>WABI-SABI 本是日文中佗寂之美的意思，指一种残缺的、不圆满的日式美学，现在已用来概括一种极简、素雅的风格。毕业于美国萨凡纳设计艺术学院家具设计专业的 Eny Lee Parker 设计了这款 The WABI-SABI Mirror &amp;Table，将桌子和镜子结合到一款设计中，并且两者不能独立存在，比如镜子如果没有桌子支撑就无法立起来，圆滚滚的桌子不插上镜子就会滚动，组合起来才完美。这是她的最新作品，还未发售，可以关注</span><a href=\"http://www.enyleeparker.com/\" target=\"_blank\">她个人网站</a><span>的更新。\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135750dOf9A4kaFIYy5ntX.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.32231405\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060613575136lgFxyuUzZtQoeq.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135751JYkPKOEUpdyljST0.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135751JtLhfMGK8w6puWQP.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.41666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span> \r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span> \r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span> \r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n</span>\n\n\n"}